title: Jonathan Swift Gulliver's Travels classic readings.
description:
Jonathan Swift Gulliver's Travels 
read by Anthony Quayle and Michael Redgrave (Vinyl, Abridged)

Gulliver's Travels A Voyage to Lilliput read by Anthony Quayle Caedmon TC 2053 (1971) 2XLP Running time 2 hours 2 mins.

Just archived these. Classic readings of a great Story. Ancient LP's so occasional crackle.
